    SIGN_OUT: 'SIGN_OUT',
    SIGN_UP_START: 'SIGN_UP_START',
    SIGN_UP_SUCCESS: 'SIGN_UP_SUCCESS',
    EDIT_DETAILS_START:'EDIT_DETAILS_START',
    EDIT_DETAILS_SUCCESS:'EDIT_DETAILS_SUCCESS',
